item.title: Project 1: Formula One Exploratory Data Analysis
item.description: In this project I will be using two datasets containing information from Formula One (F1) Racing dating from 1950-2018. The first dataset is called "results" and contains the results of over 1000 race with over 23,000 data points. This data set has variables including every driver, constructor, race, fastestlaptime, points, finishing position, etc.The second dataset is called "qualifying1" and contains data from the qualifying sessions of all of the same races as in the previou dataset.
